title: 2BR 1BA Inner Sunset apartment with parking
posting_body: ['Top Floor 2 BR Apt in Inner Sunset.', 'Kitchen with white cabinets, range hood, granite countertops, electric stove, refrigerator and laminate flooring.', 'Good sized pantry closet space.', 'Kitchen opens up to living room.', 'Living room is of good size with natural light and windows.', 'Bedrooms also of good size with closet space.', 'Bathroom with skylight.', 'Coin operated laundry machines in the building.', 'Rent includes one parking space in the shared garage.', 'Conveniently located in Inner Sunset District, few minutes away from shops, restaurants, and banks.', 'No pets.', 'No smoking.', 'To schedule a showing, please contact Dennis Etorma (DRE 01708583) at', 'show contact info', '.', 'For more available listings, please check our website at <URL>', 'C&D Realty Corporation (License number: 02096305)', 'Owner pays water and garbage.', 'Tenant pays PG&E and other services incurred.', 'Must have good credit, and 3x rent income.', '1 yr lease minimum.', 'Monthly rent $ 3,450.00 Security deposit $5,175.00', "First month's rent plus security deposit due upon signing of the lease."]
